## Before submitting an update

- Every description is 100 words or less (script checks).
- Deadlines accurate; flag "verify on official site" if unclear.
- No closed or ineligible calls in the Opportunities sheet.
- Every row has a gender category.
- File saves properly (close other uses if Excel says it's locked).
